      "content": "thanks, that helps a bit. but you mentioned it's like they're \"talking\" to each other. i heard einstein called it \"spooky action at a distance\" because it seems so weird. can you explain why it's considered so \"spooky\" or counterintuitive compared to how things normally work?",
